archimate:DataObject.name: SoftwareSupportPackage
archimate:DataObject.documentation: A SofwareSupportPackage represents the package acquired by a consumer from a software vendor. It can be materialized as one or several files (data) downloaded online or copied on a physical support. It contains all files required for deployment and installation such as installation manager and at minimum; one of the files constitutes the set of machine readable instructions that will be executed automatically after it is installed.
